    <p>{`You might be wondering why we provide `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`onMountProps`}</inlineCode>{` to the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Map`}</inlineCode>{` component if all it does with them is pass them on as second argument to the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`onMount`}</inlineCode>{` function. Wouldn’t it be cleaner to `}<a parentName="p" {...{
